strings.Value: [Attack] "I don't need the likes of you here!"
"You f-failed. You c-couldn't resist spilling blood. A pity. But this is not the last trial."
"F-Find brother Puja the W-Wolf on {g|Talon Peak}T-Talon Peak{/g}. He will tell you what to do next."
"I, I... I'm n-n-not adept at talking. Ask my brothers and sisters. They can explain b-better than me."

"My teacher named me so. It means 'a branch'. And unicorns are th-those who... W-We know how to rein in monsters because..." {n}Visaka takes a deep breath.{/n} "You know, I was once a r-r-real monster. B-But I pacified myself. Now my soul is at p-peace, and I s-share this peace with others."
"S-So long, Your Highness. May there be peace in your heart."
{n}Visaka casts a spell, and boundless peace and tranquility descend upon you. Unable to even reach for your weapon, you watch Visaka leave.{/n}
"Y-You did great. Didn't shed a drop of blood. Very few could do that."
"Rejected the false and found peace... I could tell a similar story about myself."
"That's a v-very r-radical way to p-pacify oneself, heh heh!"
